; Regression test for issue #854: -v should map to --version, not --verbose
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/854
; Before the fix, -v mapped to --verbose, so "ledger -v bal" produced a
; balance report. After the fix, -v maps to --version and exits immediately.

2024/01/01 Test transaction
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

; -v means --version: shows version info and exits with code 0.
; Redirect stdout to /dev/null since version string is build-dependent.
test -v >/dev/null
end test

; --verbose still works correctly with balance report
test --verbose bal 2>/dev/null
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
